    A SortedSet which maintains the ordering of its elements, according to either their natural order or an explicit Comparator.

    This collection is backed by a TreeSet, restricted to a maximum size (defaulted to Long.MAX_VALUE, with items being dropped from the end of the backing collection.

    Most methods (with the exception of the addition logic) are delegated to the backing collection.
